<td style="padding: 0px 25px 15px 25px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: thin; border-bottom-color: #b2d6d3; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;" colspan="2"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; line-height: 1.2; color: #000000;">Team - </span>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">For those who may be unaware, today is Pivotal's first year anniversary. Happy first birthday to everyone!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">I am extremely proud of the hard work and effort that went into Q1. As part of a publicly traded company, I can't at the moment comment on specifics. What I can say is that it is incredibly important that we build on the strong finish in Q1. Momentum is one of the keys to our success moving forward this year. The company, and I personally, have every confidence that we will meet and exceed the objectives set forth at our WWSKO.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">In pursuit of that growth, and as tangible evidence of our evolution, we will, at 12:00am PST, announce the release and launch of Pivotal Big Data Suite. This global debut will change not only the way Big Data is consumed and utilized, but its economics.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">Our aggressively priced "Mega Bundle" pulls together the best of Pivotal's data offerings and enables customers to store anything, analyze everything and build the right thing. They will be able to use the technologies that are best for their business without fear of penalty or waste of investment. No more betting the farm on the unknown. This potential speed bump in the selling process has now been flattened.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">It is hard to imagine any vendor that focuses on just one technology like Hadoop delivering the value we have in Pivotal Big Data Suite.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">I want to extend sincere thanks to everyone who has worked tirelessly to bring us to this launch.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">My ask is simple, get very familiar with the content located at </span><span style="color: #000000;">Inside Pivotal/Field Enablement<a href="https://sites.google.com/a/gopivotal.com/inside-pivotal-data-services/2014-data-services">/Inside Pivotal Data</a></span><span style="color: #000000;">. It has detail on the components of the Suite, with data sheets, an FAQ, and useful tools that will be helpful in your conversations with customers. In order to hit growth targets, we have to immediately get this story out. In addition to gathering details, put your learning to use - tell the story and the value proposition of this new package.&nbsp;We can never have enough pipeline.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">I want you to absorb the kind of advantage Pivotal Big Data Suite is going to provide. For us and for our customers, this is a mutually beneficial birthday gift.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">Make it Happen.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">- sa</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
